(138, 1, '2013-03-05 14:26:40', '2013-03-05 13:26:40', 'Les astronomes poétisants sont bien joyeux.\r\nLa journée est radieuse la place pleine de soleil.\r\nSur la vérandah ils sont penchés.\r\nMusique et amour. La dame trop belle\r\nJe voudrais mourir pour ses yeux de velours.\r\n<div style="padding: 0 0 24px 48px;">Un peintre a peint une énorme cheminée rouge\r\nQu’un poète adore comme une divinité.\r\nJ’ai revu cette nuit de printemps et de cadavres\r\nLe fleuve charriait des tombeaux qui ne sont plus.\r\nQui veut vivre encore? Les promesses sont plus belles.</div>\r\n<video width="640" height="480" controls="controls" autoplay="autoplay" preload="auto" loop="loop"><source src="http://batraz.wp.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/poland.mp4" type="video/mp4" /><source src="http://batraz.wp.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/poland.webm" type="video/webm" /><source src="http://batraz.wp.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/poland.ogv" type="video/ogg" /><object width="640" height="480" classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0"><param name="src" value="http://batraz.wp.local/wp-includes/js/tinymce/plugins/media/moxieplayer.swf" /><param name="flashvars" value="url=/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/poland.mp4&amp;poster=/wp-admin/" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="true" /><embed width="640" height="480" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" src="http://batraz.wp.local/wp-includes/js/tinymce/plugins/media/moxieplayer.swf" flashvars="url=/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/poland.mp4&amp;poster=/wp-admin/" allowfullscreen="true" allowscriptaccess="true" /></object>Video not playing? <a href="http://batraz.wp.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/poland.mp4">Download file</a> instead.</video>\r\n\r\nOn a hissé tant de drapeaux sur la gare\r\nPourvu que l’horloge ne s’arrête pas\r\nUn ministre doit arriver.\r\nIl est intelligent et doux il sourit\r\nIl comprend tout et la nuit à la lueur d’une lampe fumante\r\nPendant que le guerrier de pierre dort sur la place obscure\r\nIl écrit des lettres d’amour tristes et ardentes.', 'Poland', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'poland-2', '', '', '2013-04-05 17:09:48', '2013-04-05 15:09:48', '', 0, 'http://batraz.wp.local/?page_id=138', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(139, 1, '2013-03-05 12:03:20', '2013-03-05 11:03:20', 'A tutti i folli.\r\nI solitari.\r\nI ribelli.\r\n\r\n[shift right="150"]\r\nQuelli che non si adattano.\r\nQuelli che non ci stanno.\r\nQuelli che sembrano sempre fuori luogo.\r\nQuelli che vedono le cose in modo differente.\r\nQuelli che non si adattano alle regole. E non hanno rispetto per lo status quo.\r\n[/shift]\r\n\r\n<video width="640" height="480" controls="controls" autoplay="autoplay" preload="auto" loop="loop"><source src="http://batraz.wp.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/gizmo.mp4" type="video/mp4" /><source src="http://batraz.wp.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/gizmo.webm" type="video/webm" /><source src="http://batraz.wp.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/gizmo.ogv" type="video/ogg" /><object width="640" height="480" classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0"><param name="src" value="http://batraz.wp.local/wp-includes/js/tinymce/plugins/media/moxieplayer.swf" /><param name="flashvars" value="url=/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/gizmo.mp4&amp;poster=/wp-admin/" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="true" /><embed width="640" height="480" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" src="http://batraz.wp.local/wp-includes/js/tinymce/plugins/media/moxieplayer.swf" flashvars="url=/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/gizmo.mp4&amp;poster=/wp-admin/" allowfullscreen="true" allowscriptaccess="true" /></object>Video not playing? <a href="http://batraz.wp.local/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/gizmo.mp4">Download file</a> instead.</video>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nPotete essere d''accordo con loro o non essere d''accordo.\r\nLi potete glorificare o diffamare.\r\nL''unica cosa che non potete fare è ignorarli.\r\n\r\nPerché cambiano le cose.\r\nSpingono la razza umana in avanti.\r\nE mentre qualcuno li considera dei folli, noi li consideriamo dei geni.\r\n\r\nPerché le persone che sono abbastanza folli da pensare di poter cambiare il mondo sono coloro che lo cambiano davvero.', 'Gizmo', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'gizmo', '', '', '2013-03-06 11:39:31', '2013-03-06 10:39:31', '', 0, 'http://batraz.wp.local/?page_id=139', 0, 'page', '', 0),
